  "schema:description": "The cpdb BioBrick contains data from 6,540 chronic animal cancer tests on 1,547 chemicals, primarily sourced from NCI/NTP bioassays and scientific literature. This dataset includes TD50 potency values, target organ information, species/strain details, carcinogenicity opinions, and SMILES strings, making it valuable for toxicology research, drug discovery safety assessments, and environmental risk analysis.",
